  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Prepare the white bread mix according to package instructions and set aside.",
    "In a large skillet, saute the chopped onion and sliced mushrooms in melted butter until tender.",
    "Add the grated carrots to the skillet and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the prepared white bread mix, sauteed onion and mushroom mixture, shredded cheddar cheese, beaten eggs, and whole milk.",
    "Mix well to combine and pour into a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Bake for 35 minutes or until the top is golden brown and the casserole is set.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool for 10 minutes before serving."
  ],
